na mudança, e viu o meu?

33
00:02:00,871 --> 00:02:03,624
Sim. Barbicha!

34
00:02:03,707 --> 00:02:06,544
Cara do incêndio!

35
00:02:06,627 --> 00:02:10,130
Oi, Kevin.
