96
00:05:29,788 --> 00:05:31,165
Ouça...

97
00:05:31,790 --> 00:05:34,168
Me desculpe pelo que disse antes.

98
00:05:35,794 --> 00:05:39,506
-Passei dos limites.
-Passou mesmo.

99
00:05:39,715 --> 00:05:41,675
Mas quero recompensar.

100
00:05:42,301 --> 00:05:46,555
