216
00:12:08,145 --> 00:12:09,896
SÉTIMA SEMANA
11 DE AGOSTO

217
00:12:14,443 --> 00:12:15,944
-Olha. Raspei o cavanhaque.
-Olho.

218
00:12:16,027 --> 00:12:19,030
